  <title>Topic Layout Page</title>
  <body>
    <p>This layout page is used to generate HTML pages for each DITA topic in the WebHelp Responsive
      output. The name of the template file is <filepath>wt_topic.html</filepath> and it is located
      in the following directory:
      <codeblock outputclass="language-ini"><term keyref="glossentry_dita_ot_dir"/>/plugins/<abbreviated-form keyref="glossentry-wh-plugin-dir"/>/templates/dita/bootstrap/</codeblock></p>
    <p>The HTML pages produced for each topic consist of the topic content along with various other
      additional components, such as a title, menu, navigation breadcrumb, print icon, or side table
      of contents.</p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <title>Examples of Topic Page Components</title>
        <image href="../img/webhelp_topic_page.PNG" id="image_ubg_yjp_kv" placement="inline"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
